FQ726 *                                                                                             
FQ726 *  Si activo parámetro, Muestro pantalla de confirmación                                      
FQ726C                   IF        P2AEDFO='1'                                                      
FQ726C                             And T3EDFO<>'1'                                                  
FQ726C                             And ZXPRIM=1                                                     
FQ726C                   EXFMT     W01                                                              
FQ726C                   IF        *IN12                                                            
FQ726C                   EVAL      ERRGRL=*ON                                                       
FQ726C                   EVAL      WRK42=*ON                                                        
FQ726C                   ELSE                                                                       
FQ726 * Si está activado el parametro de solo ED Forzada                                            
FQ726 *    Escondemos los parámetros que no se utilizan                                             
FQ726C                   EVAL      WRK50=*ON                                                        
FQ726C                   EVAL      ZXOPT2='DSP'                                                     
FQ726C                   EVAL      ZXPRIM=0                                                         
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2ALIMP=*BLANKS                                                  
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2ASTCK=*BLANKS                                                  
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2ALIME=*BLANKS                                                  
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2ALOGI=*BLANKS                                                  
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2ADIBE=*ZEROS                                                   
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2ASSTO=*BLANKS                                                  
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2ANIMF=*BLANKS                                                  
FQ726C                   EVAL      P2AADOM=*BLANKS                                                  
FQ726C                   ENDIF                                                                      
FQ726C                   ENDIF                                                                      
FQ726C     ERRGRL        CABEQ     *ON           TP2ACHK                                            
FQ726 *                                                                                             
FQ726 *  Si desactivo parámetro, Muestro todos los parámetros                                       
FQ726C                   IF        P2AEDFO<>'1'                                                     
FQ726C                             And T3EDFO='1'                                                   
FQ726C                   EVAL      WRK50=*OFF                                                       
FQ726C                   IF        ZXPRIM=1                                                         
FQ726C                   EVAL      ZXOPT2='DSP'                                                     
FQ726C                   EVAL      ZXPRIM=0                                                         
FQ726C                   ENDIF                                                                      
FQ726C                   ENDIF                                                                      
FQ726                                                                                               
FQ726 * Validar Comprobar Sobreestock                                                               
FQ726C                   IF        P2ASSTO<>*BLANKS                                                 
FQ726C                   EVAL      PECTAB='EDSS'                                                    
FQ726C                   EVAL      PECLTA=*BLANKS                                                   
FQ726C                   EVAL      PECLTA=P2ASSTO                                                   
FQ726C     KPMTAB2       CHAIN     PMTAB2                                                           
FQ726C                   IF        Not %FOUND(PMTAB2)                                               
FQ726C                             Or %FOUND(PMTAB2) And PEBAJA='1'                                 
FQ726C                   EVAL      ERRGRL=*ON                                                       
FQ726C                   EVAL      MSGER='ASG1003'                                                  
FQ726C                   EVAL      WRK33=*ON                                                        
FQ726C                   ENDIF                                                                      
FQ726C     ERRGRL        CABEQ     *ON           TP2ACHK                                            
FQ726C                   ENDIF                                                                      
