FQ765C                             OR NOT%FOUND                                                     
FQ765C                   EVAL      ERRGRL=*ON                                                       
FQ765C                   EVAL      MSGER='ASG1003'                                                  
FQ765C                   EVAL      WRK51=*ON                                                        
FQ765C                   ENDIF                                                                      
