      * SUBRUTINA CONTROL DEL FMT P30                              *                                
      *------------------------------------------------------------*                                
     C     P30MAIN       BEGSR                                                                      
     C                   DOW       ZXOPT1='P30'                                                     
     C     ZXOPT2        CASEQ     'CLR'         P30CLR                                             
     C     ZXOPT2        CASEQ     'INZ'         P30INZ                                             
     C     ZXOPT2        CASEQ     'DSP'         P30DSP                                             
     C     ZXOPT2        CASEQ     'CMD'         P30CMD                                             
     C     ZXOPT2        CASEQ     'CHK'         P30CHK                                             
